
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Lymph nodes, axilla' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Borderline, central fat hilus preserved' radio button is enabled
And 'Pathological' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Borderline, central fat hilus preserved' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Right' checkbox is enabled
Then 'Short axis diameter (SAD) in mm' input field is enabled
When I select 'Left' checkbox is enabled
Then 'Short axis diameter (SAD) in mm' input field is enabled

When I select 'Pathological' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Right' checkbox is enabled
Then 'Short axis diameter (SAD) in mm' input field is enabled
And 'Level I (lower axilla)' checkbox is enabled
And 'Level II (middle axilla)' checkbox is enabled
And 'Level III (apical axilla)' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Left' checkbox is enabled
Then 'Short axis diameter (SAD) in mm' input field is enabled
And 'Level I (below the lower edge of pectoralis minor muscle)' checkbox is enabled
And 'Level II (underneath/post. the pectoralis minor muscle)' checkbox is enabled
And 'Level III (above/medial the pectoralis minor muscle)' checkbox is enabled